    "info": "The <b>Celestial Sigil<\/b> is a boss-summoning item crafted out of 20 of each of the Celestial Pillar's fragments. It is used to summon the Moon Lord without going through the Lunar Events. The Lunar Events must not be active (there cannot be Celestial Pillars in the world) to use the item. This item cannot be used when you are able to see any Lunatic Devote and\/or Blue Cultist Archer on your screen, or when another boss has already been summoned. It also cannot be used in a world in which Golem has not been defeated or if there is another event going on, like the Pirate Invasion. Note that rather than summoning the Moon Lord immediately after the item is used, it takes a minute before the Moon Lord actually appears, the same way as when all of the pillars are defeated.\n",
